<L>__{interior prayer room, norbulinka night}
<A>__{the nechung oracle is in full swing. it is an especially vivid and violent spin he is in. the headdress whips this way and that, and finally he says:}
<C>__{nechung oracle}
<D>__{where there is no crossing a big river, no fords, no shallows, where the only hope is a boat, and there is no boat... i will put a boat, kundun. the wish fulfilling jewel will shine from the west.}
<A>__{it is a strange and confusing prophecy.}
